Requires manual download of static data from: https://developer.translink.ca/ServicesGtfs/GtfsData

Additional feeds are provided for arrivals at a given stop, stop locations, and a trip planner. Additional fields are contained in static data as well, documentation available at: https://developer.trimet.org/gtfs_ext.shtml
No realtime feeds are provided per GTFS specification, only information about stop summaries and trips for a particular stop
